Web Portal for CLient

The portal has been developed based on the CodeIgniter framework. The following where developed by me exclusively:
css:
	gportal.css
	login.css
images
views:
	about.php
	audit.php - not ready for production
	database.php
	home.php 
	login.php
	management.php
	more_info.php
	price_list.php - not ready for production
	quality_control_management.php
	tools.php
	user_area.php
Controllers:
	gportal_ctrl.php
	login.php
Models:
	access_mdl.php
	database_mdl.php
libraries:
	Business.php
	Database_search.php
	
	
The web portal connects to a database which contains all the data that the tool attempts to obtain and display, the database was developed in MySQL and was also developed by me.
